title: This Week - S13E14 - 2015.01.08 - 468p x264
description:
POLITICAL: This Week
On: BBC 1 HD     
Date: Thursday 8th January 2015 
Time: 23:40 to 00:25 

Andrew Neil presents  

Andrew Neil presents a review of the political week and film on the terrorist attacks in Paris and the political ramifications; with Michael Portillo and guests. Journalist Simon Jenkins explains why he thinks politicians have gone mad trying to pretend they can heal the NHS with a little extra money. And former BBC broadcaster Richard Bacon says why he is one of the few feeling positive and cheerful about the start of the longest-ever general election campaign. The panel for the first programme of 2015 sees Diane Abbott, Michael Portillo and Miranda Green help review the political week. Crack open the Blue Nun and prepare to watch public service broadcasting at its best.
